dct_title_s: [Parts of France, Belgium, Luxembourg, parts of Germany]
dct_description_sm: Extrait de la carte de France <<A. Taride >> ; Printed at Base Printing Plant, 29th. Engineers, U.S. Army 1919.
Cities and towns, land routes, boundaries, waterways, sea routes (and approximate time to travel).
Probably taken from atlas "Operations of American divisions in France," 1919.
